  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\n@truffle/hdwallet-provider [specifies ethereumjs-util@6](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/develop/packages/hdwallet-provider/package.json#L29). This uses an older version of @types/bn.js which aren't compatible with the new types incorporated by #5177, a breaking change rolled out in [Truffle's latest patch-level release](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/releases/tag/v5.5.20). \r\n",
